Estimated production, net imports, and apparent consumption of timber products in the US, 1900-1962

=======

Estimated production, net imports, and apparent consumption of timber products in the US, 1900-1962

>>>>>>> master

Dataset containing estimated statistics for timber products. All vectors are numeric. Most data is for products in the Industrial Roundwood Class. Each column except the first two and the last one are in this category.

hair1963
<<<<<<< HEAD

Format

A data frame with 85 observations on 38 variables

    =======

    Format

    A data frame with 85 observations on 38 variables

      >>>>>>> master
    • Dom.Prod.Tot Total Domestic Production
    • ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption
    • Dom.Prod Domestic Production, Total Ind RW
    • Imports Net Imports, Total Ind RW
    • Prod.SW Softwood Production, Total Ind RW
    • Prod.HW Hardwood Production , Total Ind RW
    • LogChipImports.SW Softwood Log and Chip Imports, Total Ind RW
    • LogChipExports.SW Softwood Log and Chip Exports, Total Ind RW
    • LogChipImports.HW Hardwood Log and Chip Imports, Total Ind RW
    • LogChipExports.HW Hardwood Log and Chip Exports, Total Ind RW
    • SW.PctOfProd Softwoods as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • Exports.SW.PctOfProd Softwood Exports as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • Exports.HW.PctOfProd Hardwood Exports as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • Imports.SW.PctOfConsump Softwood Imports as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • Imports.HW.PctOfConsump Hardwood Imports as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • SW.Lumber.PctOfTotLumbProd Softwood Lumber as Percent of Total Lumber Production, Total Ind RW
    • DV.Exports.Log.PctOfProd Dollar Value of Log Exports as Percent of Production, Total Ind RW
    • DV.Imports.Log.PctOfConsump Dollar Value of Log Imports as Percent of Consumption, Total Ind RW
    • Estimated.Imports Estimated Imports, Total Ind RW
    • Estimated.Exports Estimated Exports, Total Ind RW
    • Adj.Imports Adjusted Imports, Total Ind RW
    • Adj.Exports Adjust Exports, Total Ind RW
    • Estimated.Imports(tons) Estimated Imports in tons, Total Ind RW
    • Estimated.Exports(tons) Estimated Exports in tons, Total Ind RW
    • Adj.Imports(tons) Adjusted Imports in tons, Total Ind RW
    • Adj.Exports(tons) Adjust Exports in tons, Total Ind RW
    • ApparentConsumption.Total Apparent Conusmption, Total Ind RW. Columns may not add to total because of rounding.
    • SawLogs.Dom.Prod Domestic Production of Saw Logs
    • SawLogs.NetImports Net Imports of Saw Logs. Net imports of lumber converted to cubic feet roundwood. Small quantities of imported saw logs (roundwood form) are included under domestic production.
    • SawLogs.ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption of Saw Logs. Columns may not add to total because of rounding. Includes changes in stocks beginning in 1935.
    • VeneerLogs.Dom.Prod Domestic Production of Veneer Logs
    • VeneerLogs.NetImports Net Imports of Veneer Logs. Net imports of veneer logs represent the equivalent net imports of veneer and plywood converted to board feet log scale, and then to cubic feet round-wood. The small volume of veneer logs imported (roundwood form) is included under domestic production.
    • VeneerLogs.ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption of Veneer Logs. Columns may not add to total because of rounding.
    • PulpWood.Dom.Prod Domestic Production of Pulpwood
    • PulpWood.NetImports Net Imports of Pulpwood
    • PulpWood.ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption of Pulpwood
    • Other.ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption of Other Products
    • FuelWood.ApparentConsumption Apparent Consumption of Fuelwood
